dm_disallow:
:thinking: You can't listen music in DirectMessage ;(
But I can be your wordless companion \:)
help_help: shows this page now you're looking at
leave_help: stops the ongoing stream and leaves the voice channel
leave_no_voice: :thinking: I'm not on any channels already!
leave_success: :hand_splayed: I stopped ongoing stream and left the channel!
leave_force_question_1: :grey_question: It's on `%1$s` already! Do you still want to get me out?
leave_force_question_2: :grey_question: Someone else is listening to Lofi on `%1$s`. Do you still want to get me out?
leave_force_fail_1: :octagonal_sign: There's someone listening on the `%1$s`. I can't get out
leave_force_fail_2: :octagonal_sign: There's someone listening on the `%1$s`. I can't get out
mark_help: you can set up a channel to play Lo-Fi all the time.
mark_no_permission:
:rolling_eyes: uh... `%1$s`, you don't have permissions to set channels!
In order to use this command, you must have at least `manage channels` permissions
mark_select_voice: please select voice channel to play Lo-Fi all the time.
mark_select_voice_placeholder: click here to select a voice channel.
mark_select_not_exist: channel `%1$s` does not exist or is not a voice channel.
mark_not_joinable: :microphone2: um.. I can't get into that voice channel. :(
mark_not_speakable: :zipper_mouth: I don't have permission to speak on that voice channel. :(
mark_success:
:ok_hand: I set it to play on `%1$s`!
*tip: you can play right now using `%2$splay`
*tip: you can choose different theme using `%2$stheme`
unmark_no_permission:
:rolling_eyes: uh... `%1$s`, you don't have permissions to set channels!
to use this command, you must have `manage channels` permissions to use at least
unmark_success: channel configuration has been deleted. you can set configuration with `%1$smark` command again.
ping_help: Measure and show the delay of the communication.
play_help: Play a Lo-Fi stream with a preset theme
play_no_voice: :loudspeaker: Enter the voice channel you want to play and try again
play_not_joinable: :microphone2: um.. I can't get into that voice channel. :(
play_not_speakable: :zipper_mouth: I don't have permission to speak on that voice channel. :(
play_select_voice: please select voice channel to play
play_select_voice_placeholder: click here to select a voice channel.
play_select_not_exist: channel `%1$s` does not exist or is not a voice channel.
play_force_question: :grey_question: already playing on `%1$s`! Shall I move?
play_theme_fail: :octagonal_sign: theme settings are corrupted... please reset your theme preset with `%1$stheme`
theme_help: you can change the Lo-Fi theme I'm going to play
theme_play_force_question:
:grey_question: already turned on at `%1$s`, do you want change theme immediately?
*if you don't want it, theme will changed when all listeners are left
theme_play_force_fail: :grey_exclamation: already turned on at `%1$s`, I'll change theme when all listeners are left
